<heading>list - Show running flows.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  list
  list --all
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Lists all active flows (jobs) in the current session.

By default only foreground and suspended flows are shown.
Add --all to include background and completed flows.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
bg, stop, fg, man
</paragraph>
